name: Lawquanes
content:
The Lawquanes were a family located on the planet Saleucami. The adoptive father of the family was Cut Lawquane, a former clone trooper. He worked as a farmer and had married Suu. The two children of the family were Jek Lawquane and Shaeeah Lawquane.
During the Battle of Saleucami, Cut joined with Clone Captain CT-7567 "Rex" to defend their home from BX-series droid commandos.
During the Clone Wars, Cut was a clone trooper in the Galactic Republic's Grand Army. Following the Battle of Geonosis, Cut's troop transport came under attack by several Separatist gunships and crashed. When the battle droids searched the transport's wreckage, Cut ran away knowing that he would not survive. He eventually made his way to the Outer Rim planet of Saleucami. There, he met, fell in love and married Suu Lawquane. Together, they raised Suu's children, Shaeeah and Jek at their farmstead.
